310 void PrmFile::init(const char* name) {
311  Parser* prs = new Parser(name); // TODO memory leak
312  len = prs -> length();
313  buf = prs -> address();
314 
315  int i = 0,mode = 1;
316  char c;
317  while(i < len){
318  c = buf[i];
319  if(c == '\"'){
320  buf[i++] = '\0';
321  while(i < len){
322  if(buf[i] == '\"') break;
323  i++;
324  }
325  if(i == len) ErrH.Abort("Wrong PRM format, second <\"> is absent");
326  else buf[i] = '\0';
327  }
328  else
329  if(c == ' ' || c == '\t' || c == '\r' || c == ',' || c == '\n') buf[i] = '\0';
330  i++;
331  }
332  i = 0;
333  while(i < len){
334  c = buf[i];
335  if(mode){ if(c == '/' && buf[i + 1] == '*'){ buf[i] = '\0'; mode = 0; } }
336  else {
337  if(c == '*' && buf[i + 1] == '/'){ buf[i] = buf[i + 1] = '\0'; i++; mode = 1; }
338  else if(c != '\n') buf[i] = '\0';
339  }
340  i++;
341  }
342  index = 0;
343 }
344 
345 char* PrmFile::getAtom(void){
346  char* p = buf + index;
347  while(index < len && !(*p)) p++, index++;
348  if(index == len) return NULL;
349  char* ret = p;
350  while(index < len && *p) p++, index++;
351  return ret;
352 }
353 
354 void listElem::link(listElem*& tail){
355  if(!tail) {
356  tail = this;
357  } else {
358  tail -> prev -> next = this;
359  prev = tail -> prev;
360  }
361  next = NULL;
362  tail -> prev = this;
363 }
364 
365 void uvsElement::elink(uvsElement*& tail){
366  if(!tail) tail = this;
367  else {
368  tail -> eprev -> enext = this;
369  eprev = tail -> eprev;
370  }
371  enext = NULL;
372  tail -> eprev = this;
373 }
374 
375 void uvsElement::delink(uvsElement*& tail){
376  if( tail == this) tail = this -> enext;
377  if(eprev -> enext) eprev -> enext = enext;
378  if(enext){
379  enext -> eprev = eprev;
380  } else if ( tail ){
381  tail -> eprev = eprev;
382  }
383  if( tail ) tail -> eprev -> enext = NULL;
384 }
385 
386 void uvsElement::eunlink(uvsElement*& tail){
387  if(this == tail) tail = enext;
388  if(eprev -> enext) eprev -> enext = enext;
389  if(enext) enext -> eprev = eprev;
390 }

392 listElem* listElem::seekName(const char* name){
393  listElem* p = this;
394  char* s;
395  while(p){
396  s = p -> GetName();
397  if(!strcmp(name,s)) return p;
398  p = p -> next;
399  }
400  return NULL;
401 }

403 int getRW(int n){
404  int r = n;
405 
406  while( r == n )
407  r = RND(MAIN_WORLD_MAX);
408 
409  return r;

412 void uniVangPrepare(void){
413  std::cout<<"uniVangPrepare"<<std::endl;
414  uvsEscave* pe;
415  PrmFile pfile;
416  char* atom;
417  int i;
418 
419  aci_curLocationName = "";
420  uvsLastEscaveName = "";
421  DollyIndex = 1;
422  uvsQuantFlag = 0;
423  uvsPoponkaID = RND(DG_POPONKA_MAX);
424  uniVangDelete();
425 
426  CurrentWorld = 0;
427 
428  if (NetworkON){
429  NetStatisticInit();
430  NetStatisticGameStart();
431 
432  RNDVAL = my_server_data.InitialRND|1;
433 
434  switch (my_server_data.GameType){
435  case VAN_WAR:
436  break;
437  case MECHOSOMA:
438  break;
439  case PASSEMBLOSS:
440  break;
441  case HUNTAGE:
442  break;
443  case MUSTODONT:
444  uvsUnikumeMechos = 0;
445  break;
446  };
447  }
448 
449  uvsTownName = NULL;
450  // item initing
451  pfile.init(PrmFileName[6]);
452  if(strcmp(PrmSignature,pfile.getAtom())) ErrH.Abort(PrmWrongMsg,XERR_USER,-1,PrmFileName[6]);
453 
454  MAX_ITEM_TYPE = atoi(pfile.getAtom());
455  uvsItemTable = new uvsItemType*[MAX_ITEM_TYPE];
456 
457  for( i = 0; i < MAX_ITEM_TYPE; i++){
458  uvsItemTable[i] = new uvsItemType(&pfile);
459  }// end for i
460  pfile.finit();
461 
462  // worlds initing
463  pfile.init(PrmFileName[0]);
464  if(strcmp(PrmSignature,pfile.getAtom())) ErrH.Abort(PrmWrongMsg,XERR_USER,-1,PrmFileName[0]);
465  uvsWorld* pw;
466  while((atom = pfile.getAtom()) != NULL) (pw = new uvsWorld(&pfile,atom)) -> link(WorldTail);
467  pfile.finit();
468 
469  // escaves initing
470  pfile.init(PrmFileName[1]);
471  if(strcmp(PrmSignature,pfile.getAtom())) ErrH.Abort(PrmWrongMsg,XERR_USER,-1,PrmFileName[1]);
472  while((atom = pfile.getAtom()) != NULL) (pe = new uvsEscave(&pfile,atom)) -> link(EscaveTail);
473  pfile.finit();
474 
475  // spots initing
476  pfile.init(PrmFileName[2]);
477  if(strcmp(PrmSignature,pfile.getAtom())) ErrH.Abort(PrmWrongMsg,XERR_USER,-1,PrmFileName[2]);
478  uvsSpot* ps;
479  while((atom = pfile.getAtom()) != NULL) (ps = new uvsSpot(&pfile,atom)) -> link(SpotTail);
480  pfile.finit();
481 
482  // passages initing
483  pfile.init(PrmFileName[3]);
484  if(strcmp(PrmSignature,pfile.getAtom())) ErrH.Abort(PrmWrongMsg,XERR_USER,-1,PrmFileName[3]);
485  uvsPassage* pp;
486  while((atom = pfile.getAtom()) != NULL) (pp = new uvsPassage(&pfile,atom)) -> link(PassageTail);
487  pfile.finit();
488 
489 // mechos initing
490  pfile.init(PrmFileName[7]);
491  if(strcmp(PrmSignature,pfile.getAtom())) ErrH.Abort(PrmWrongMsg,XERR_USER,-1,PrmFileName[7]);
492 
493  MAX_MECHOS_MAIN = atoi(pfile.getAtom());
494  MAX_MECHOS_RAFFA = atoi(pfile.getAtom());
495  MAX_MECHOS_CONSTRACTOR = atoi(pfile.getAtom());
496  MAX_MECHOS_TYPE = MAX_MECHOS_MAIN + MAX_MECHOS_RAFFA + MAX_MECHOS_CONSTRACTOR;
497  uvsMechosTable = new uvsMechosType*[MAX_MECHOS_TYPE];
498 
499  for( i = 0; i < MAX_MECHOS_TYPE; i++){
500  uvsMechosTable[i] = new uvsMechosType(&pfile);
501  }// end for i
502  pfile.finit();
503 
504  // TabuTask Initing
505  MAX_TABUTASK = 0;
506  pfile.init(PrmFileName[10]);
507  if(strcmp(PrmSignature,pfile.getAtom())) ErrH.Abort(PrmWrongMsg,XERR_USER,-1,PrmFileName[10]);
508  uvsTabuTaskType* pt;
509  while((atom = pfile.getAtom()) != NULL) (pt = new uvsTabuTaskType(&pfile,atom)) -> link(TabuTaskTypeTail);
510  pfile.finit();
511 
512  if (_pe_) _pe_ -> TabuTaskCount = MAX_TABUTASK - _pe_ -> TabuTaskID;
513  if (_ps_) _ps_ -> TabuTaskCount = MAX_TABUTASK - _ps_ -> TabuTaskID;
514 
515  _ps_ = NULL;
516  _pe_ = NULL;
517 
518  TabuTable = new uvsTabuTaskType*[MAX_TABUTASK];
519  pt = (uvsTabuTaskType*)TabuTaskTypeTail;
520  for( i = 0; i < MAX_TABUTASK; i++){
521  TabuTable[i] = pt;
522  pt = (uvsTabuTaskType*)pt -> next;
523  }
524  // stationary objects linking
525  pw = (uvsWorld*)WorldTail;
526  int __t = 1;
527  int _t = 1;
528  while(pw) {
529  i = 0;
530  if (pw->escTmax) {
531  if (pw->escT != NULL) {
532  delete[] pw->escT;
533  }
534  pw->escT = new uvsEscave*[pw->escTmax];
535  pe = (uvsEscave*)EscaveTail;
536  while(pe){
537  if (__t)
538  pe -> link_good();
539  if(pe -> Pworld == pw){
540  if ( i == pw -> escTmax ) ErrH.Abort(PrmWrongMsg,XERR_USER,-1,"escave graiter when MAX");
541  pw -> escT[i++] = pe;
542  }
543  pe = (uvsEscave*)pe -> next;
544  }
545  __t = 0;
546  }
547  i = 0;
548  if (pw -> sptTmax){
549  pw -> sptT = new uvsSpot*[pw -> sptTmax];
550  ps = (uvsSpot*)SpotTail;
551  while(ps){
552  if (_t)
553  ps -> link_good();
554  if(ps -> Pworld == pw) {
555  if ( i == pw -> sptTmax ) ErrH.Abort(PrmWrongMsg,XERR_USER,-1,"spot graiter when MAX");
556  pw -> sptT[i++] = ps;
557  }
558  ps = (uvsSpot*)ps -> next;
559  }
560  _t = 0;
561  }
562  i = 0;
563  pw -> pssT = new uvsPassage*[pw -> pssTmax];
564  pp = (uvsPassage*)PassageTail;
565  while(pp){
566  if(pp -> Pworld == pw) {
567  if ( i == pw -> pssTmax ) ErrH.Abort(PrmWrongMsg,XERR_USER,-1,"passage graiter when MAX");
568  pw -> pssT[i++] = pp;
569  }
570  pp = (uvsPassage*)pp -> next;
571  }
572  pw = (uvsWorld*)pw -> next;
573  }
574 
575  //znfo генерация итемов в мире
576  for( i = 0; i < MAX_ITEM_TYPE; i++){
577  if ( uvsItemTable[i] -> type == UVS_ITEM_STATUS::WEAPON) {
578 #ifdef ALL_ITEM_IN_SHOP
579  if(1)
580 #else
581  if (i == UVS_ITEM_TYPE::MACHOTINE_GUN_LIGHT ||
582  i == UVS_ITEM_TYPE::SPEETLE_SYSTEM_LIGHT ||
583  i == UVS_ITEM_TYPE::GHORB_GEAR_LIGHT )
584 #endif
585  for( int j = 0; j < MAIN_WORLD_MAX; j++) WorldTable[j] -> generate_item( i );
586  else
587  WorldTable[RND(3)] -> generate_item( i );
588 
589  } else if (uvsItemTable[i] -> type == UVS_ITEM_STATUS::DEVICE){
590 
591 #ifdef ALL_ITEM_IN_SHOP
592  for( int j = 0; j < MAIN_WORLD_MAX; j++) WorldTable[j] -> generate_item( i );
593 #else
594 
595  switch(i){
596  case UVS_ITEM_TYPE::COPTE_RIG:
597  WorldTable[2] -> generate_item( i );
598  break;
599  case UVS_ITEM_TYPE::CROT_RIG:
600  WorldTable[0] -> generate_item( i );
601  break;
602  case UVS_ITEM_TYPE::CUTTE_RIG:
603  WorldTable[1] -> generate_item( i );
604  break;
605  case UVS_ITEM_TYPE::RADAR_DEVICE:
606  WorldTable[RND(3)] -> generate_item( i );
607  break;
608  }// end switch
609 #endif
610  } else
611  for( int j = 0; j < MAIN_WORLD_MAX; j++) WorldTable[j] -> generate_item( i );
612  }// end for i
613 
614  // bunches initing
615  pfile.init(PrmFileName[4]);
616  if(strcmp(PrmSignature,pfile.getAtom())) ErrH.Abort(PrmWrongMsg,XERR_USER,-1,PrmFileName[4]);
617  uvsBunch* pb;
618  while((atom = pfile.getAtom()) != NULL) (pb = new uvsBunch(&pfile,atom)) -> link(BunchTail);
619  pfile.finit();
620 
621  currentVanger = 1;
622  // vangers initing
623  pfile.init(PrmFileName[5]);

849 void uvsRestoreVanger(void){
850 #ifdef _ROAD_
851  uvsElement* p = ETail;
852  uvsVanger* v;
853 
854  v = Gamer;
855  if (!NetworkON) {
856  if( v -> Pescave) {
857  addVanger(v,v->Pescave, 1);
858  } else {
859  addVanger(v,v->Pspot, 1);
860  }
861  } else {
862  if( v -> Pescave ){
863  int x, y;
864  NetworkGetStart(v -> Pescave -> name, x, y);
865  addVanger(v,x,y, 1);
866  }else{
867  int x, y;
868  NetworkGetStart(v -> Pspot -> name, x, y);
869  addVanger(v,x, y, 1);
870  }
871  }
872  while(p){
873  if(p -> type == UVS_OBJECT::VANGER ){
874  v = (uvsVanger*)p;
875  if ( v -> shape != UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER ){
876  if(v -> Pworld -> gIndex == CurrentWorld && (v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::MOVEMENT
877  || v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::FREE_MOVEMENT
878  || v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::AIM_HANDLE
879  || v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::RACE_HUNTER
880  || v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::GATHERING
881  || v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::WAIT_GAMER
882  || v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::RACE)){
883 
884  if ( v -> Pmechos -> color < 3 &&
885  WorldTable[v -> Pmechos -> color] -> escT[0] -> Pbunch -> status == UVS_BUNCH_STATUS::UNABLE &&
886  v -> shape != UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER_SLAVE){
887  v -> Pmechos -> color = 3;
888  if(v -> shape == UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::BUNCH_SLAVE)
889  v -> shape = UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::RANGER;
890  }
891  addVanger(v,v -> pos_x,v -> pos_y);
892  }
893  }
894  }
895  p = p -> enext;
896  }
897  StartWTRACK();
898 #endif
899 }

901 void uvsWorldReload(int newW){
902 #ifdef _ROAD_
903  uvsElement* p = ETail;
904  uvsVanger* v;
905  while(p){
906  if(p -> type == UVS_OBJECT::VANGER && ((uvsVanger*)p) -> shape != UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER){
907  v = (uvsVanger*)p;
908  if(v -> Pworld -> gIndex == newW && (v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::MOVEMENT
909  || v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::FREE_MOVEMENT
910  || v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::AIM_HANDLE
911  || v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::RACE_HUNTER
912  || v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::GATHERING
913  || v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::WAIT_GAMER
914  || v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::RACE)){
915 
916  if ( v -> Pmechos -> color < 3 &&
917  WorldTable[v -> Pmechos -> color] -> escT[0] -> Pbunch -> status == UVS_BUNCH_STATUS::UNABLE &&
918  v -> shape != UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER_SLAVE){
919  v -> Pmechos -> color = 3;
920  if(v -> shape == UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::BUNCH_SLAVE)
921  v -> shape = UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::RANGER;
922  }
923  addVanger(v,v -> pos_x,v -> pos_y);
924  }
925  }
926  p = p -> enext;
927  }
928  CurrentWorld = newW;
929  if (WorldTable[CurrentWorld]-> escTmax){
930  uvsCurrentCycle = WorldTable[CurrentWorld] -> escT[0] -> Pbunch -> currentStage;
931 
932  if (Gamer -> Pworld -> escT[0] -> Pbunch -> status == UVS_BUNCH_STATUS::UNABLE)
933  uvsCurrentWorldUnable = 1;
934  else
935  uvsCurrentWorldUnable = 0;
936  } else {
937  uvsCurrentCycle = 0;
938  uvsCurrentWorldUnable = 0;
939  }
940 
941  if (NetworkON && WorldTable[CurrentWorld]-> escTmax){
942  uvsBunch* pb = WorldTable[CurrentWorld]-> escT[0] -> Pbunch;
943 
944  pb -> cycleTable[pb -> currentStage].cirtQ = pb -> cycleTable[pb -> currentStage].cirtMAX;
945  sBunchSend(pb -> id, pb -> cycleTable[pb -> currentStage].cirtQ, pb -> currentStage);
946  }
947 
948  StartWTRACK();
949 #endif
950 }

995 void uvsContimer::Quant(void){
996  counter++;
997  if(++sec == 60){
998  sec = 0;
999  listElem* l = BunchTail;
1000  while(l){
1001  ((uvsBunch*)l) -> QuantCirt(counter);
1002  l = l -> next;
1003  }
1004 
1005  if(++min == 60){
1006  min = 0;
1007 
1008  if (hour & 0x00000001){
1009  GamerResult.dominance--;
1010  ShowDominanceMessage(-1);
1011  if (GamerResult.dominance < -100) GamerResult.dominance = -100;
1012  }
1013 
1014  if(NetworkON)
1015  Gamer -> Pworld -> updateResource();
1016 
1017  l = EscaveTail;
1018  while(l){
1019  ((uvsEscave*)l) -> QuantChange(hour);
1020  l = l -> next;
1021  }
1022 
1023  if(++hour == 24){
1024  hour = 0;
1025  ++day;
1026 
1027  if (day == 1000)
1028  day = 0;
1029 
1030  if ((day&3) == 0)
1031  uvsRestoreTabuTask();
1032  }
1033  }
1034  }
1035 }

1037 char* uvsContimer::GetTime(void){
1038  sTime.init();
1039  //sTime < uvsStrings[0] < strdup(" ") <= day < strdup(", ");//zmod2005
1040  sTime < "Day " <= day < ", ";
1041  if(hour < 10) sTime < "0";
1042  sTime <= hour < ":";
1043  if(min < 10) sTime < "0";
1044  sTime <= min < ":";
1045  if(sec < 10) sTime < "0";
1046  sTime <= sec;
1047  return sTime.GetBuf();
1048 }

1834 void uvsShop::get_list_from_ActInt( uvsActInt*& Mechos, uvsActInt*& Item){
1835  uvsActInt* pa;
1836  uvsItem* pl;
1837  int dead_world = (Gamer -> Pworld -> escT[0] -> Pbunch -> status == UVS_BUNCH_STATUS::UNABLE);
1838  //Pmechos = NULL;
1839 
1840  int first_constr = MAX_MECHOS_TYPE - MAX_MECHOS_CONSTRACTOR;
1841  pa = Mechos;
1842  while(pa){
1843  if (Mechos -> type >= first_constr ){
1844  int _type = Mechos -> type - first_constr;
1845  Mechos -> type = first_constr + (_type>>2);
1846  _type &= 3;
1847  uvsMechosTable[Mechos -> type] -> constractor = _type;
1848  }
1849  (new uvsMechos( Mechos -> type )) -> link( Pmechos );
1850  Mechos = (uvsActInt*)Mechos -> next;
1851  delete (uvsActInt*)pa;
1852  pa = Mechos;
1853  }
1854  Mechos = NULL;
1855 
1856  pa = Item;
1857  while(pa){
1858  int tmp_type = ActInt_to_Item( Item -> type);
1859 
1860  if ( uvsItemTable[ tmp_type ] -> type != UVS_ITEM_STATUS::GOODS){
1861  (pl = new uvsItem( tmp_type )) -> link( Pitem );
1862 
1863  if (pl -> type == UVS_ITEM_TYPE::CONLARVER || dead_world){
1864  pl -> param1 = Item -> param1;
1865  pl -> param2 = Item -> param2;
1866  }
1867  } else {
1868  if (tmp_type == UVS_ITEM_TYPE::ELEEPOD ||
1869  tmp_type == UVS_ITEM_TYPE::BEEBOORAT ||
1870  tmp_type == UVS_ITEM_TYPE::ZEEX){
1871  if (Gamer -> Pescave )
1872  Gamer -> Pescave -> PassagerWait = 0;
1873  else
1874  Gamer -> Pspot -> PassagerWait = 0;
1875  }// end if
1876  }// end if
1877

1886 void uvsVanger::addInventory(void){
1887 // DBGCHECK;
1888  int i;
1889  uvsItem *pi;
1890  char* ItemHere;
1891 
1892  if (Pescave)
1893  ItemHere = Pescave -> Pshop -> ItemHere;
1894  else

1896

1898

1901  if(!addItem(pi)) delete pi;

1904  if(!addItem(pi)) delete pi;
1905

1908

1911  addItem(pi, 1);
1912  }
1913  }

1916  while(!ItemHere[i]){
1917  i = RND(6);
1918  }

1920

1922  ((uvsItem*)pi) -> type = 0;
1923  if(!addItem(pi)) delete pi;
1924  }
1925

1929  i = RND(6);
1930  }
1931  pi = new uvsItem(i);
1932  } else {
1933  pi = new uvsItem(UVS_ITEM_TYPE::TERMINATOR);
1934  }

1944  shape == UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::CARAVAN ||
1945  shape == UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::RANGER ||
1946  shape == UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::THIEF)
1947  && (ItemHere[UVS_ITEM_TYPE::RADAR_DEVICE])
1948  ){
1949  pi = new uvsItem(UVS_ITEM_TYPE::RADAR_DEVICE);
1950 
1951  if(!addItem(pi)) delete (uvsItem*)pi;

1956 void uvsTabuTaskType::activateVANGER(void){
1957  uvsVanger *pv = FindFreeVanger();
1958 
1959  switch(work_on_target){
1960  case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::GO_OUT:
1961  pv -> goNewEscave();
1962 
1963  if (pv -> Pescave){
1964  pv -> pos_x = pv -> Pescave -> pos_x + 1024;
1965  pv -> pos_y = pv -> Pescave -> pos_y;
1966  }else{
1967  pv -> pos_x = pv -> Pspot -> pos_x + 1024;
1968  pv -> pos_y = pv -> Pspot -> pos_y;
1969  }
1970 
1971  pv -> status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::FREE_MOVEMENT;
1972  Ptarget = (uvsTarget*)pv;
1973  break;
1974  case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::KILL:
1975  if (pv -> Pescave){
1976  pv -> set_target(pv -> Pworld -> sptT[0], UVS_TARGET::SPOT);
1977 
1978  pv -> pos_x = pv -> Pescave -> pos_x + 1024;
1979  pv -> pos_y = pv -> Pescave -> pos_y;
1980 
1981  }else{
1982  pv -> set_target(pv -> Pworld -> escT[0], UVS_TARGET::ESCAVE);
1983  pv -> pos_x = pv -> Pspot -> pos_x + 1024;
1984  pv -> pos_y = pv -> Pspot -> pos_y;
1985  }
1986 
1987  pv -> addInventory();
1988  pv -> status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::FREE_MOVEMENT;
1989  Ptarget = (uvsTarget*)pv;
1990  break;
1991  case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::DEFENSE:
1992  if (pv -> Pescave)
1993  pv -> set_target(pv -> Pescave, UVS_TARGET::ESCAVE);
1994  else
1995  pv -> set_target(pv -> Pspot, UVS_TARGET::SPOT);
1996 
1997  pv -> pos_x = pv -> Pworld -> pssT[0] -> pos_x + 1024;
1998  pv -> pos_y = pv -> Pworld -> pssT[0] -> pos_y;
1999 
2000  pv -> addInventory();
2001  pv -> status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::FREE_MOVEMENT;
2002  Ptarget = (uvsTarget*) pv;
2003  break;
2004  };
2005 }

2185 void uvsTabuTaskType::activate(void){
2186  int i;
2187 
2188  if (status == UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::ACTIVE) return;
2189 
2190  status = UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::ACTIVE;
2191 
2192  switch( target ){
2193  case UVS_TARGET::RACE:
2194  break;
2195  case UVS_TARGET::DOLLY:
2196  *real_count = 0;
2197  activateDOLLY();
2198  break;
2199  case UVS_TARGET::VANGER:
2200  *real_count = 0;
2201  activateVANGER();
2202  break;
2203  case UVS_TARGET::VANGERS:
2204  case UVS_TARGET::ESCAVE:
2205  case UVS_TARGET::SPOT:
2206  case UVS_TARGET::PASSAGE:
2207  case UVS_TARGET::ITEM:
2208  case UVS_TARGET::FLY_FARMER:
2209  case UVS_TARGET::BEEB:
2210  case UVS_TARGET::GRIB:
2211  case UVS_TARGET::HIVE:
2212  case UVS_TARGET::CRYPT:
2213  case UVS_TARGET::WHIRLPOOL:
2214  case UVS_TARGET::SWAMP:
2215  case UVS_TARGET::SHEILD:
2216  case UVS_TARGET::RAFFA:
2217  for( i = 0; i < item_number; i++)
2218  real_count[i] = 0;
2219  break;
2220  case UVS_TARGET::NONE:
2221  break;
2222  };
2223 }

2355 void uvsShop::prepare_list_for_ActInt( uvsActInt*& Mechos, uvsActInt*& Item, int where){
2356  listElem* pe;
2357  listElem* pb;
2358  listElem* pn;
2359  listElem* pl;
2360  uvsActInt* pd = NULL;
2361  uvsBunch *pm;
2362  int cq, mq;
2363  int priceQ;
2364  int color = -1;
2365  int raffa_on = 0;
2366  int dead_world = (Gamer -> Pworld -> escT[0] -> Pbunch -> status == UVS_BUNCH_STATUS::UNABLE);
2367  int m_count = 0;
2368 
2369 #ifdef TOTAL_CASH
2370  aciUpdateCurCredits(799999);
2371 #endif
2372 
2373  char* lm = new char[MAX_MECHOS_TYPE];
2374  char* li = new char[MAX_ITEM_TYPE];
2375 
2376  memset( lm, 0, MAX_MECHOS_TYPE);
2377  memset( li, 0, MAX_ITEM_TYPE);
2378 
2379  pb = NULL;
2380  pe = Pmechos;
2381 
2382  if (WorldTable[ CurrentWorld ] -> escTmax){
2383  pm = WorldTable[ CurrentWorld ] -> escT[0] -> Pbunch;
2384  color = CurrentWorld;
2385 
2386  cq = pm -> cycleTable[ pm -> currentStage ].cirtQ;
2387  mq = pm -> cycleTable[ pm -> currentStage ].cirtMAX;
2388  priceQ = pm -> cycleTable[ pm -> currentStage ].priceQ;
2389  } else {
2390  pm = NULL;
2391  cq = mq = 1;
2392  priceQ = 100;
2393  }
2394 
2395  while( pe ){
2396  m_count++;
2397  if ( uvsMechosTable[((uvsMechos*)pe) -> type] -> type == UVS_CAR_TYPE::RAFFA )
2398  raffa_on = 1;
2399 #ifdef _DEMO_
2400  if (CAR_DEMO[((uvsMechos*)pe) -> type])
2401 #endif
2402  if ( (!lm[((uvsMechos*)pe) -> type]) || dead_world){
2403  pn = new uvsActInt;
2404 
2405  int first_constr = MAX_MECHOS_TYPE - MAX_MECHOS_CONSTRACTOR;
2406 
2407  if (( ((uvsMechos*)pe) -> type) >= first_constr){
2408  int _type = ( ((uvsMechos*)pe) -> type) - first_constr;
2409  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> type = first_constr + (_type<<2) + uvsMechosTable[( ((uvsMechos*)pe) -> type)] -> constractor;
2410 
2411  if (uvsMechosTable[( ((uvsMechos*)pe) -> type)] -> constractor == 3)
2412  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price = uvsMechosTable[( ((uvsMechos*)pe) -> type)] -> price;
2413  else
2414  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price = 1;
2415  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price = uvsMechosTable[( ((uvsMechos*)pe) -> type)] -> sell_price;
2416  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> param1 = color;
2417  } else {
2418  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> type = ( ((uvsMechos*)pe) -> type);
2419 
2420  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price = uvsMechosTable[( ((uvsMechos*)pe) -> type)] -> price;
2421  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price = uvsMechosTable[( ((uvsMechos*)pe) -> type)] -> sell_price;
2422  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> param1 = color;
2423  }
2424 
2425  if (((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price != 1 && !NetworkON){
2426  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price = (((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price*1.5*cq + ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price*(mq-cq))/mq;
2427  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price = (((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price*cq + ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price*0.5*(mq-cq))/mq;
2428 
2429  double t = ((double)(GamerResult.dominance+GamerResult.add_dominance))/100.0;
2430 
2431  if ( t > 1.0 ) t = 1.0;
2432  if ( t < -1.0 ) t = -1.0;
2433 
2434  if ( t > 0.0 ){
2435  double dt = ( ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price - ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price)/2.0;
2436  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price -= t*dt;
2437  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price += t*dt;
2438  } else {
2439  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price *= (1.0 - t);
2440  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price *= (1.0 + t);
2441  }
2442 
2443  if (((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price > ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price) ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price = ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price;
2444 
2445  if (dead_world)

3497  sptT[i] -> Pshop -> updateResource();
3498

3500  sptT[i] -> PassagerWait++;
3501

4497 void uvsVanger::set_target(uvsTarget* pt, int _type){
4498  uvsOrder* ord = orderT; // первый элемент
4499  switch(_type){
4500  case UVS_TARGET::ESCAVE:
4501  ord -> type = UVS_ORDER::MOVING;
4502  ord -> event = UVS_EVENT::GO_ESCAVE;

4504  ord -> Ptarget = pt;
4505  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::MOVEMENT;
4506  break;
4507  case UVS_TARGET::SPOT:
4508  ord -> type = UVS_ORDER::MOVING;
4509  ord -> event = UVS_EVENT::GO_SPOT;
4510  ord -> target = _type;
4511  ord -> Ptarget = pt;
4512  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::MOVEMENT;
4513  break;
4514  case UVS_TARGET::VANGER:
4515  ord -> type = UVS_ORDER::MOVING;
4516  ord -> event = UVS_EVENT::GO_KILL;
4517  ord -> target = _type;
4518  ord -> Ptarget = pt;
4519  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::MOVEMENT;
4520  break;
4521  case UVS_TARGET::VANGERS:
4522  case UVS_TARGET::PASSAGE:
4523  case UVS_TARGET::DOLLY:
4524  case UVS_TARGET::ITEM:
4525  case UVS_TARGET::BEEB:
4526  case UVS_TARGET::GRIB:
4527  case UVS_TARGET::HIVE:
4528  case UVS_TARGET::CRYPT:
4529  case UVS_TARGET::WHIRLPOOL:
4530  case UVS_TARGET::SWAMP:
4531  case UVS_TARGET::SHEILD:
4532  case UVS_TARGET::NONE:
4533  ErrH.Abort("uvsVanger::set_target : go nothing");
4534  break;
4535  case UVS_TARGET::FLY_FARMER:
4536  ord -> type = UVS_ORDER::MOVING;
4537  ord -> event = UVS_EVENT::GO_CORN;
4538  ord -> target = _type;
4539  ord -> Ptarget = pt;

4545 int uvsVanger::addItem(uvsItem* pi, int w ){
4546  int l_box[4];
4547  int k_box[4];
4548  int i;
4549 
4550  if ( !w ){
4551  memset(l_box, 0, sizeof(int)*4);
4552  listElem* pe = Pitem;
4553 
4554  // проверка загруженности
4555 
4556  while(pe){
4557  l_box[uvsItemTable[((uvsItem*)pe) -> type] -> size]++;
4558 
4559  pe = pe -> next;
4560  }
4561 
4562  l_box[ uvsItemTable[((uvsItem*)pi) -> type ] -> size]++;
4563 
4564  memcpy(k_box, uvsMechosTable[Pmechos -> type] -> box, sizeof(int)*4 );
4565 
4566  for(i = 0; i < 4; i++){
4567  if( l_box[i] > k_box[i])
4568  return 0;
4569  else if ( i != 3) k_box[i+1] += k_box[i] - l_box[i];
4570  }
4571  }
4572  pi -> link(Pitem);
4573  return 1;
4574 }

4803 void uvsVanger::save(XStream& pfile){

4805  pfile < gIndex;

4821  count++;

4834  if(Pspot) put_string(pfile, Pspot -> name); else pfile < ((char)0);

4838  pfile < pos_y;

4870  break;

4872  pfile < ((char)0);

5088 #endif

5100  pa -> delink(GGamer);
5101  delete pa;

5107  uvs_aciKillItem(uvsItemTable[ pi -> type ] -> SteelerTypeFull);
5108 
5109  while(pi){
5110 
5111  ((uvsItem*)pi) -> delink( Pitem );
5112  delete pi;
5113  pi = GetItem( Pitem, GoodsType, 0 );
5114  }
5115  }// if count
5116

5118  }// if GoodsType != -1
5119  return 0;

5595 void uvsVanger::Quant(void){
5596  uvsCultGame* pg;
5597 
5598  c_All_Number++;
5599  switch(shape){
5600  case UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::BUNCH_SLAVE:
5601  c_S_Number++;
5602  switch(status){
5603  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::GAME_BEGIN_ESCAVE:
5604  if ( Pescave -> locked || (--locTimer > 0)) break;
5605  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::RACE;
5606 #ifdef _ROAD_
5607  if(isActive()) addVanger(this,Pescave);
5608 #endif
5609  break;
5610  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::GAME_HUNTER_BEGIN_ESCAVE:
5611  if ( !Pescave -> real_hunter_now(this) || (--locTimer > 0) ) break;
5612  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::RACE_HUNTER;
5613 #ifdef _ROAD_
5614  if(isActive()) addVanger(this,Pescave);
5615 #endif
5616  break;

5620 #ifdef _ROAD_
5621  if(isActive()) addVanger(this,Pspot);
5622 #endif
5623  break;
5624  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::GAME_HUNTER_BEGIN_SPOT:

5639  add_to_game(pg);

5642  } else {

5644  }

5647  owner -> randVRes();
5648 #ifdef _ROAD_

5650 #endif
5651  }
5652  break;

5655  if(Pspot -> game_soon() && !RND(3)){
5656  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::SPOT_WAITING;

5671  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::RACE:
5672  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::RACE_HUNTER:

5674  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::WAIT_GAMER:
5675  break;

5743  Event(UVS_EVENT::GO_FROM_ESCAVE);
5744  else
5745  Event(UVS_EVENT::GO_NEW_ESCAVE);
5746  if (status != UVS_VANGER_STATUS::ESCAVE_SLEEPING)
5747  owner -> randVRes();
5748 #ifdef _ROAD_
5749  if(isActive()) addVanger(this,Pescave);
5750 #endif
5751  }
5752  break;
5753  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::SPOT_SLEEPING:
5754  if(isBunchReady() && (!Pspot -> locked)){
5755 // if(!Pspot -> locked){
5756  if(Pspot -> game_soon()){
5757  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::SPOT_WAITING;
5758  break;
5759  } else if (Pspot -> game_now(pg))
5760  add_to_game(pg);
5761  else if (shape != UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::THIEF && !RND(48)){
5762 // else if (shape != UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::THIEF && !RND(2)){
5763  thief_from_spot(Pspot);
5764  } else
5765  Event(UVS_EVENT::GO_FROM_SPOT);
5766 
5767  if (status != UVS_VANGER_STATUS::SPOT_SLEEPING)
5768  owner -> randVRes();
5769 #ifdef _ROAD_
5770  if(isActive()) addVanger(this,Pspot);
5771 #endif
5772  }
5773  break;
5774  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::MOVEMENT:
5775  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::FREE_MOVEMENT:
5776  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::RACE:
5777  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::RACE_HUNTER:
5778  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::GATHERING:
5779  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::WAIT_GAMER:
5780 
5781  break;
5782  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::PASSAGE_GAP:
5783  if(!--locTimer){
5784  if(makeJump()){
5785 #ifdef _ROAD_
5786  if(isActive()) addVanger(this,Ppassage);
5787 #endif
5788  }
5789  else locTimer = 1;
5790  }
5791  break;
5792  }
5793  break;
5794  case UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::TABUTASK:
5795  switch(status){
5796  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::SPOT_SLEEPING:
5797  Event(UVS_EVENT::GO_FROM_SPOT);
5798 
5799  if (status != UVS_VANGER_STATUS::SPOT_SLEEPING)
5800  owner -> randVRes();
5801 #ifdef _ROAD_
5802  if(isActive()) addVanger(this,Pspot);
5803 #endif
5804  break;
5805  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::ESCAVE_SLEEPING:
5806  if(!RND(2))
5807  Event(UVS_EVENT::GO_FROM_ESCAVE);
5808  else
5809  Event(UVS_EVENT::GO_NEW_ESCAVE);
5810 
5811  if (status != UVS_VANGER_STATUS::ESCAVE_SLEEPING)
5812  owner -> randVRes();
5813 #ifdef _ROAD_
5814  if(isActive()) addVanger(this,Pescave);
5815 #endif
5816  break;
5817  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::MOVEMENT:
5818  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::FREE_MOVEMENT:
5819  break;
5820  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::PASSAGE_GAP:
5821  if(!--locTimer){
5822  if(makeJump()){
5823 #ifdef _ROAD_
5824  if(isActive()) addVanger(this,Ppassage);
5825 #endif
5826  } else locTimer = 1;
5827  }
5828  break;
5829  };// end switch
5830  break;
5831  case UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::KILLER:
5832  switch(status){
5833  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::MOVEMENT:
5834  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::FREE_MOVEMENT:
5835  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::WAIT_GAMER:
5836  break;
5837  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::PASSAGE_GAP:
5838  if(!--locTimer){
5839  if(makeJump()){
5840 #ifdef _ROAD_
5841  if(isActive()) addVanger(this,Ppassage);
5842 #endif
5843  } else locTimer = 1;
5844  }
5845  break;
5846  }// end switch
5847  break;
5848  case UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER:
5849  switch(status){
5850 #ifdef _ROAD_
5851  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::GO_NEW_WORLD:
5852  /*{
5853  Pworld -> getItemFromCrypt(UVS_CRYPT::DEVICE);
5854  Pworld -> getItemFromCrypt(UVS_CRYPT::AMMO);
5855  Pworld -> getItemFromCrypt(UVS_CRYPT::ARMO_LIGHT);
5856  Pworld -> getItemFromCrypt(UVS_CRYPT::ARMO_HEAVY);
5857  } else {
5858  Pworld -> updateCrypt();
5859  }*/
5860 
5861  EffectsOff();
5862 
5863  Pworld -> GamerVisit++;
5864 
5865  if (WorldTable[Pworld -> gIndex]-> escTmax){
5866  uvsCurrentCycle = WorldTable[Pworld -> gIndex] -> escT[0] -> Pbunch -> currentStage;
5867  if (Gamer -> Pworld -> escT[0] -> Pbunch -> status == UVS_BUNCH_STATUS::UNABLE)
5868  uvsCurrentWorldUnable = 1;
5869  else
5870  uvsCurrentWorldUnable = 0;
5871  } else {
5872  uvsCurrentCycle = 0;
5873  uvsCurrentWorldUnable = 0;
5874  }
5875 
5876  if (WorldTable[Pworld -> gIndex] -> escTmax)
5877  aci_curLocationName = WorldTable[Pworld -> gIndex] -> escT[0] -> name;
5878  else
5879  aci_curLocationName = "";
5880 
5881  ChangeWorld(Pworld -> gIndex); // смена мира
5882  addVanger(this,pos_x, pos_y,1); // человек
5883  uvsWorldReload(Pworld -> gIndex);
5884  if ( !Pworld -> GamerVisit ){
5885  ShowDominanceMessage(10);
5886  GamerResult.dominance += 10;
5887  if (GamerResult.dominance > 100) GamerResult.dominance = 100;
5888  }
5889 
5890 
5891 #ifdef STAND_REPORT
5892  stand < ConTimer.GetTime();
5893  stand < "\nTeleport on the World " < Pworld -> name < " visit " <= Pworld -> GamerVisit < "\n";
5894 #endif
5895  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::MOVEMENT;
5896  break;
5897 #endif
5898  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::GO_NEW_ESCAVE:
5899  Pworld -> GamerVisit++;
5900 
5901  if (WorldTable[Pworld -> gIndex]-> escTmax){
5902  uvsCurrentCycle = WorldTable[Pworld -> gIndex] -> escT[0] -> Pbunch -> currentStage;
5903  if (Gamer -> Pworld -> escT[0] -> Pbunch -> status == UVS_BUNCH_STATUS::UNABLE)
5904  uvsCurrentWorldUnable = 1;
5905  else
5906  uvsCurrentWorldUnable = 0;
5907  } else {
5908  uvsCurrentCycle = 0;
5909  uvsCurrentWorldUnable = 0;
5910  }
5911

5913  if ( !Pworld -> GamerVisit ){
5914  ShowDominanceMessage(10);
5915  GamerResult.dominance += 10;
5916  if (GamerResult.dominance > 100) GamerResult.dominance = 100;
5917  }
5918 #ifdef STAND_REPORT
5919  stand < ConTimer.GetTime();
5920  stand < "\nTeleport on the World " < Pworld -> name < " visit " <= Pworld -> GamerVisit < "\n";
5921 #endif
5922  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::SHOPPING;
5923  locTimer = 1;
5924  break;
5925  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::MOVE_TO_MECHOS:
5926  ChangeVanger();
5927  addVanger(this,pos_x, pos_y,1); // человек
5928  uvsWorldReload(Pworld -> gIndex);
5929  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::MOVEMENT;
5930  break;
5931  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::PASSAGE_GAP:
5932  if(!--locTimer) makeJump();
5933  break;
5934  case UVS_VANGER_STATUS::SHOPPING:
5935 #ifdef _ROAD_
5936  if(--locTimer) break;
5937  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::IN_SHOP;
5938  GameQuantReturnValue = RTO_ESCAVE_ID;
5939 #endif
5940  break;
5941  }
5942  break;
5943  case UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER_SLAVE:
5944  break;
5945  }

5948 //znfo event (for bots?)
5949 void uvsVanger::Event(UvsEventType ev){
5950 
5951  switch(ev){
5952  case UVS_EVENT::THIEF:
5953  thief_from_escave(Pescave);
5954  break;
5955  case UVS_EVENT::THIEF_FROM_SHOP:
5956  thief_from_shop(Pescave -> Pshop);
5957  break;
5958  case UVS_EVENT::GO_FROM_ESCAVE:
5959  go_from_escave();
5960  break;
5961  case UVS_EVENT::GO_FROM_SPOT:
5962  go_from_spot();
5963  break;
5964  case UVS_EVENT::GO_CIRT:
5965  goCirt();
5966  break;
5967  case UVS_EVENT::GO_NEW_ESCAVE:
5968  if (shape == UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER)
5969  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::GO_NEW_ESCAVE;
5970  else
5971  goNewEscave();
5972  break;
5973  case UVS_EVENT::SPOT_ARRIVAL:
5974  spotArrival();
5975  if ( shape != UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER ){
5976  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::SPOT_SLEEPING;
5977  }else {
5978  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::SHOPPING;
5979  locTimer = LOC_TIME;
5980  }
5981  break;
5982  case UVS_EVENT::ESCAVE_ARRIVAL:
5983  homeArrival();
5984  if ( shape != UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER ){
5985  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::ESCAVE_SLEEPING;
5986  } else {
5987  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::SHOPPING;
5988  locTimer = LOC_TIME;
5989  }
5990  break;
5991  case UVS_EVENT::PASSAGE_ARRIVAL:
5992  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::PASSAGE_GAP;
5993  if ( shape != UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER ){
5994  shiftOrders();
5995  }
5996  locTimer = shape == UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER ? 1 : V_PGAP_TIME;
5997  break;
5998  case UVS_EVENT::AIM_ARRIVAL:
5999  aimHandle();
6000  break;
6001  case UVS_EVENT::FATALITY:
6002  destroy();
6003  break;
6004  case UVS_EVENT::GO_NEW_WORLD:
6005  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::GO_NEW_WORLD;
6006 
6007  break;
6008  };
6009 }

6051  ord -> target = UVS_TARGET::SPOT;

6187 int uvsVanger::buildWay(uvsWorld* fromW,uvsWorld* toW){
6188  uvsWorld* nextW,*tmpW = NULL;
6189  uvsWorld *lastfromW = NULL, *lasttoW = NULL;
6190  uvsOrder* ord;
6191  uvsPassage* pp;
6192  int i = 0;
6193 
6194  if (fromW -> gIndex >= MAIN_WORLD_MAX ) {
6195  lastfromW = fromW;
6196  fromW = fromW -> pssT[0] -> Poutput;
6197 
6198  ord = orderT;
6199  ord -> type = UVS_ORDER::MOVING;
6200  ord -> event = UVS_EVENT::GO_PASSAGE;
6201  ord -> target = UVS_TARGET::PASSAGE;
6202  ord -> Ptarget = (uvsTarget*)lastfromW -> pssT[0];
6203  i = 1;
6204  }
6205 
6206  if (toW -> gIndex >= MAIN_WORLD_MAX ) {
6207  lasttoW = toW;
6208  toW = toW -> pssT[0] -> Poutput;
6209  }
6210 
6211  unsigned int linkage = ChainMap[toW -> gIndex + fromW -> gIndex*MAIN_WORLD_MAX],mI;
6212 
6213  if ( fromW == toW ) return 0;
6214 
6215  for(; i < 8; i++){
6216  mI = (linkage & (0x0000000F << 4*i)) >> 4*i;
6217  nextW = getWorld(mI);
6218 
6219  if(!nextW) nextW = toW;
6220  pp = fromW -> getPassage(nextW);
6221 
6222  if ( !pp ) ErrH.Abort( "buildWay:: not passage");
6223 
6224  ord = orderT + i;
6225  ord -> type = UVS_ORDER::MOVING;
6226  ord -> event = UVS_EVENT::GO_PASSAGE;
6227  ord -> target = UVS_TARGET::PASSAGE;
6228  ord -> Ptarget = (uvsTarget*)pp;
6229  fromW = nextW;
6230 
6231  if ( fromW == toW ) break;
6232  }
6233 
6234  i++;
6235  if ( lasttoW ){
6236  pp = fromW -> getPassage(lasttoW);
6237  ord = orderT + i;
6238  ord -> type = UVS_ORDER::MOVING;
6239  ord -> event = UVS_EVENT::GO_PASSAGE;
6240  ord -> target = UVS_TARGET::PASSAGE;
6241  ord -> Ptarget = (uvsTarget*)pp;
6242  i++;
6243  }
6244 
6245  return (i);
6246 }

6248 void uvsVanger::goCirt(void){
6249  uvsItem* pi;
6250  uvsDolly* pdl = owner -> cycleTable[owner -> currentStage].Pdolly;
6251 
6252  if ( !(Pmechos -> status & UVS_MECHOS_USED::HARVEST) ) return;
6253 
6254  if ( pdl -> Pworld -> gIndex > 3 ) return;
6255 
6256  addInventory();
6257 
6258  if (pdl -> status == UVS_DOLLY_STATUS::CATCH){
6259  if (!RND(10) && uvsKillerNow() < 2)
6260  go_to_GAMER();
6261  else return;
6262  } else {
6263  pi = new uvsItem(UVS_ITEM_TYPE::CIRTAINER);
6264  if (!addItem(pi, 0)) {
6265  delete pi;
6266  return;
6267  }
6268 
6269  uvsWorld* fromW = Pworld;
6270  uvsWorld* toW = pdl -> Pworld;
6271  int offset;
6272  uvsOrder* ord;
6273 
6274  offset = buildWay(fromW,toW);
6275 
6276  ord = orderT + offset;
6277  ord -> type = UVS_ORDER::CIRT_GATHERING;
6278  ord -> event = UVS_EVENT::GO_CIRT;
6279  ord -> target = UVS_TARGET::DOLLY;
6280  ord -> Ptarget = (uvsTarget*)pdl;
6281 
6282  status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::MOVEMENT;
6283  }
6284  //cirtStage = owner -> currentStage;
6285 }

6307 int uvsVanger::prepare_killer(void){
6308 
6309  if ( !(Pescave -> Pbunch -> status & ((int)(UVS_BUNCH_STATUS::KILL_GAMER))) ) return 0;
6310 
6311  if (uvsKillerNow() >= 2) return 0;
6312 
6313  if ( status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::ESCAVE_SLEEPING ){
6314  Pescave -> Pshop -> sellMechos(Pmechos, (int)(UVS_MECHOS_USED::KILLER));
6315  Pmechos -> color = Pescave -> Pbunch -> biosNindex;
6316 
6317  if (Pmechos -> status & ((int)UVS_MECHOS_USED::KILLER)){
6318  shape = UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::KILLER;
6319  Pescave -> Pbunch -> status ^= (int)(UVS_BUNCH_STATUS::KILL_GAMER);
6320  addInventory();
6321  go_to_GAMER();
6322  return 1;
6323  }
6324  }
6325  return 0;
6326 }

6328 void uvsVanger::prepare_caravan(void){

6878 int uvsDolly::getCirt(int x,int y){
6879  int i;
6880  int Range = 32000;
6881  int RangeL;
6882  int tmp;
6883 
6884  if (status) return 0;
6885 
6886 #ifdef STAND_REPORT
6887  stand < "dolly index"<= gIndex < "\n";
6888  stand < "dolly bois"<= biosNindex < "\n\n";
6889 #endif
6890  for( i = 0; i < DOLLY_TAIL_LEN; i++){
6891  RangeL = int(sqrt( double((tail_x[i] - x)*(tail_x[i] - x) + (tail_y[i] - y)*(tail_y[i] - y))));
6892 
6893  if ( RangeL < Range ) {
6894  Range = RangeL;
6895  }
6896  }
6897 
6898  if ( Range >= V_CIRT_R) // 4096
6899  tmp = 0;
6900  else if ( Range >= V_CIRT_R/2) // 2048
6901  tmp = 1;
6902  else if ( Range >= V_CIRT_R/4) // 1024
6903  tmp = 2;
6904  else if ( Range >= V_CIRT_R/6) // 700
6905  tmp = 3;
6906  else if ( Range >= V_CIRT_R/8) // 512
6907  tmp = 4;
6908  else if ( Range >= V_CIRT_R/16) // 256
6909  tmp = 5;
6910  else if ( Range >= V_CIRT_R/40) // 100
6911  tmp = 6;
6912  else
6913  tmp = 7;
6914 
6915  return (tmp << (gIndex*3));
6916 }

6925 
6926  while( !out ){

6929  if( pi ){
6930  tmp += pe -> Pbunch -> addCirt(pi);
6931  ((uvsItem*)pi) -> delink(Pitem);
6932  delete (uvsItem*)pi;
6933  out = 0;
6934  }
6935  }
6936  return tmp;
6937 }

6939 int uvsBunch::addCirt(uvsItem* pi){
6940  int i = 0;
6941  int tmp = 0;
6942 
6943  for ( i = 0; i < cycleN; i++){
6944  if( (1 << cycleTable[i].Pdolly -> gIndex) & pi -> param2) {
6945  tmp += ((pi -> param1 >> (cycleTable[i].Pdolly -> gIndex*3)) & 7);
6946  cycleTable[i].cirtQ += ((pi -> param1 >> (cycleTable[i].Pdolly -> gIndex*3)) & 7);
6947  }
6948  }// end for j
6949  return tmp;
6950 }

6960  next -> prev = prev;
6961  } else if ( pe ) {
6962  pe -> prev = prev;
6963  }
6964  if( pe ) {
6965  pe -> prev -> next = NULL;
6966  }
6967 }

7304 void uvsVanger::shiftOrders(void){
7305  if(shape == UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER || NetworkON) return;
7306 
7307  uvsOrder* ord = orderT;
7308 
7309  switch ( orderT -> target ){
7310  case UVS_TARGET::NONE:
7311  ErrH.Abort("uvsVanger::shift order none");
7312  break;
7313  case UVS_TARGET::ESCAVE:
7314  Pescave = (uvsEscave*)(orderT -> Ptarget);
7315  break;
7316  case UVS_TARGET::SPOT:
7317  Pspot = (uvsSpot*)(orderT -> Ptarget);
7318  break;
7319  case UVS_TARGET::PASSAGE:
7320  Ppassage = (uvsPassage*)(orderT -> Ptarget);
7321  break;
7322  case UVS_TARGET::VANGER:
7323  break;
7324  case UVS_TARGET::ITEM:
7325  break;
7326  }// end swith
7327 
7328  for(int i = 1;i < ORDER_V_MAX; i++){;
7329  orderT[i - 1].type = orderT[i].type;
7330  orderT[i - 1].event = orderT[i].event;
7331  orderT[i - 1].target = orderT[i].target;
7332  orderT[i - 1].Ptarget = orderT[i].Ptarget;
7333  }
7334 
7335  ord = orderT + ORDER_V_MAX - 1;
7336  ord -> type = UVS_ORDER::NONE;
7337  ord -> target = UVS_TARGET::NONE;
7338  ord -> Ptarget = NULL;
7339 }

7457 void uvsVanger::emuStep(void){
7458  uvsOrder* ord = orderT;
7459 
7460 
7461  if( !speed ) ErrH.Abort("emuStep dont have speed");
7462 
7463  if(ord -> Ptarget -> pos_y > pos_y){ pos_y += speed + RND(2); pos_x += RND(5) - 2; }
7464  else if(ord -> Ptarget -> pos_y < pos_y){ pos_y -= speed + RND(2); pos_x += RND(5) - 2; }
7465  else
7466  if(ord -> Ptarget -> pos_x > pos_x) pos_x++;
7467  else if(ord -> Ptarget -> pos_x < pos_x) pos_x--;
7468 
7469 }

7510 void uvsVanger::emuCheck(void){
7511  uvsOrder* ord = orderT;
7512 
7513  if (shape == UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::KILLER){
7514  go_to_GAMER();
7515  }
7516 
7517  if(abs(ord -> Ptarget -> pos_y - pos_y) <= V_SPEED_MAX){
7518  pos_y = ord -> Ptarget -> pos_y;
7519 
7520  if ( (ord -> event == UVS_EVENT::GO_CIRT) && (abs(ord -> Ptarget -> pos_x - pos_x) <= V_CIRT_R/2)){
7521  Event(UVS_EVENT::AIM_ARRIVAL);
7522  } else if(abs(ord -> Ptarget -> pos_x - pos_x) <= V_SPEED_MAX ){
7523  pos_x = ord -> Ptarget -> pos_x;
7524  pos_y = ord -> Ptarget -> pos_y;
7525  switch(ord -> event){
7526  case UVS_EVENT::GO_SPOT:
7527  Pspot = (uvsSpot*)(orderT -> Ptarget);
7528  Event(UVS_EVENT::SPOT_ARRIVAL);
7529  break;
7530  case UVS_EVENT::GO_ESCAVE:
7531  Pescave = (uvsEscave*)(orderT -> Ptarget);
7532  Event(UVS_EVENT::ESCAVE_ARRIVAL);
7533  break;
7534  case UVS_EVENT::GO_PASSAGE:
7535  //Ppassage = (uvsPassage*)( orderT -> Ptarget);
7536  Event(UVS_EVENT::PASSAGE_ARRIVAL);
7537  break;
7538  case UVS_EVENT::GO_CORN:
7539  break;

7545  }// end switch
7546  }// end if

9284 void ReadPriceList( void ){
9285  char *atom;
9286  int i;
9287  uvsEscave* pe;
9288  uvsSpot* ps;
9289 
9290  PrmFile pfile;
9291  pfile.init(PrmFileName[8]);
9292 
9293  if(strcmp(PrmSignature,pfile.getAtom())) ErrH.Abort(PrmWrongMsg,XERR_USER,-1,PrmFileName[8]);
9294 
9295  while( 1 ){
9296  if((atom = pfile.getAtom()) == NULL) break;
9297 
9298  for( i = 0; i < MAX_ITEM_TYPE; i++)
9299  if ( !strcmp( atom, uvsItemTable[i] -> name) ) break;
9300 
9301  if ( i == MAX_ITEM_TYPE ) {
9302  pe = (uvsEscave*)EscaveTail -> seekName( atom );
9303  ps = (uvsSpot*)SpotTail -> seekName( atom );
9304 
9305  if ( !ps && !pe ) ErrH.Abort(PrmWrongMsg,XERR_USER,-1,"Bad ITEM or Town NAME");
9306  } else {
9307  if ( pe ){
9308  pe -> Pshop -> Price[i] = atoi(pfile.getAtom());
9309  pe -> Pshop -> Price[i + MAX_ITEM_TYPE] = atoi(pfile.getAtom());
9310  } else if ( ps ){
9311  ps -> Pshop -> Price[i] = atoi(pfile.getAtom());
9312  ps -> Pshop -> Price[i + MAX_ITEM_TYPE] = atoi(pfile.getAtom());
9313  } else ErrH.Abort(PrmWrongMsg,XERR_USER,-1,"None Town Name");
9314  }
9315  } // end while
9316 
9317  pfile.finit();
9318 }

9426 int uvsSetItemType(int type,int param1,int param2){
9427  if ( type == -1 ) return -1;
9428 
9429  if (type >= MAX_ITEM_TYPE)
9430  ErrH.Abort("uvsSetItemType :: type >= MAX_ITEM_TYPE");
9431 
9432  int i = uvsItemTable[type] -> SteelerTypeEmpty;
9433 
9434  if (type == UVS_ITEM_TYPE::TABUTASK){
9435  if (param2 & ((int)(UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::GOOD)<<16))
9436  return TABUTASK_GOOD;
9437 
9438  if (param2 & ((int)(UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::BAD)<<16))
9439  return TABUTASK_BAD;
9440  }
9441 
9442  if( (param1 || param2) && (uvsItemTable[type] -> type != UVS_ITEM_STATUS::GOODS))
9443  i = uvsItemTable[type] -> SteelerTypeFull;
9444  return i;
9445 }

9903 int uvsCatchDolly(uvsDolly* pd){
9904  uvsElement* p = ETail;
9905  uvsVanger* v;
9906  uvsOrder* ord;
9907 
9908  while(p){
9909  if(p -> type == UVS_OBJECT::VANGER ){
9910  v = (uvsVanger*)p;
9911  if ( v -> shape != UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER ){
9912  ord = v -> orderT;
9913 
9914  while(ord -> target == UVS_TARGET::PASSAGE) ord++;
9915 
9916  if (ord -> Ptarget == ((uvsTarget*)(pd)) )
9917  v -> go_to_GAMER();
9918  }// end if
9919  }// end if
9920  p = p -> enext;
9921  }// end while
9922  pd -> status = UVS_DOLLY_STATUS::CATCH;
9923  SOUND_LARVA()
9924 
9925  WorldTable[pd -> biosNindex] -> escT[0] -> Pbunch -> status |= (int)UVS_BUNCH_STATUS::KILL_GAMER;
9926 
9927 #ifdef STAND_REPORT
9928  stand < ConTimer.GetTime();
9929  stand < " Catch Dolly " <= pd -> gIndex < " from world " < pd -> Pworld -> name < "\n";
9930 #endif
9931 
9932  return pd -> gIndex;
9933 }

9935 int uvsFreeDolly(int _x, int _y, int _index_){
9936  listElem* pd = DollyTail;
9937 
9938  while(pd){
9939  if (((uvsDolly*)pd) -> gIndex == _index_){
9940  if (CurrentWorld > 3){
9941 // ((uvsDolly*)pd) -> status = UVS_DOLLY_STATUS::UNABLE;
9942  ((uvsDolly*)pd) -> status = 0;
9943  uvsCheckKronIventTabuTask(UVS_KRON_EVENT::KILL_DOLLY, ((uvsDolly*)pd) -> biosNindex);
9944  } else
9945  ((uvsDolly*)pd) -> status = 0;
9946 
9947  ((uvsDolly*)pd) -> Pworld = WorldTable[CurrentWorld];
9948  ((uvsDolly*)pd) -> pos_x = _x;
9949  ((uvsDolly*)pd) -> pos_y = _y;
9950  ((uvsDolly*)pd) -> setSpeed();
9951 
9952 #ifdef STAND_REPORT
9953  stand < ConTimer.GetTime();
9954  stand < " Free Dolly " <= ((uvsDolly*)pd) -> gIndex < " in world " < WorldTable[CurrentWorld] -> name < "\n";
9955 #endif
9956  GamerResult.luck -= 10;
9957  ShowLuckMessage(-10);
9958  if (GamerResult.luck < 0) GamerResult.luck = 0;
9959  return 0;
9960  }
9961  pd = pd -> next;

10295 uvsVanger* uvsMakeNewGamerInEscave(uvsEscave* pe, int what ){
10296  uvsElement* p = ETail;
10297  uvsVanger* v;
10298  uvsMechos* pm;
10299  listElem* pl;
10300 
10301 // FreeMechosList(GGamerList);
10302 
10303  while(p){
10304  if(p -> type == UVS_OBJECT::VANGER ){
10305  v = (uvsVanger*)p;
10306  if ( v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::ESCAVE_SLEEPING || v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::SPOT_SLEEPING){
10307  if (what){
10308  v -> locTimer = 1;
10309  v -> shape = UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER;
10310  v -> status = UVS_VANGER_STATUS::SHOPPING;
10311 
10312  v -> Pescave = pe;
10313  v -> Pspot = NULL;
10314  v -> Pworld = pe -> Pworld;
10315 
10316  Gamer -> shape = UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER_SLAVE;
10317  Gamer -> gIndex = v -> gIndex;
10318  v -> gIndex = 0;
10319  Gamer = v;
10320  } else
10321  pe -> Pshop -> sellMechos(Gamer -> Pmechos);
10322 
10323  pm = (uvsMechos*)pe -> Pshop -> Pmechos;
10324  pl = pe -> Pshop -> Pmechos -> next;
10325 
10326  while(pl){
10327  if (uvsMechosTable[pm -> type] -> price > uvsMechosTable[((uvsMechos*)pl) -> type] -> price)
10328  pm =(uvsMechos*)pl;
10329  pl = pl -> next;
10330  }
10331 
10332  if (((listElem*)pm) == pe -> Pshop -> Pmechos ){
10333  pe -> Pshop -> Pmechos = pe -> Pshop -> Pmechos -> next;
10334  if (pe -> Pshop -> Pmechos)
10335  pe -> Pshop -> Pmechos -> prev = pm -> prev;
10336  } else {
10337  if (pm -> next)
10338  pm -> next -> prev = pm -> prev;
10339  else
10340  pe -> Pshop -> Pmechos -> prev = pm -> prev;
10341  pm -> prev -> next = pm -> next;
10342  }
10343 
10344  pm -> type = RND(MAX_MECHOS_RAFFA) + MAX_MECHOS_MAIN;
10345  Gamer -> Pmechos = pm;
10346  if (!Gamer -> Pmechos)
10347  ErrH.Abort("uvsMakeNewGamer :: dont have any mechos in shop");
10348 
10349 // aciCurCredits -= uvsMechosTable[pm -> type] -> price;
10350 
10351 // if (aciCurCredits < 0)
10352 // aciCurCredits = 0;
10353 
10354  if (what){
10355 // aciCurCredits -= uvsMechosTable[pm -> type] -> price;
10356 /* if (!Gamer -> addItem(new uvsItem(UVS_ITEM_TYPE::SECTOR)))
10357  ErrH.Abort("uvsMakeNewGamerInEscave : dont add artifact");*/
10358  }

10360  aciUpdateCurCredits(0);
10361  return Gamer;

10363  }// end if vanger

10395 const int ELEECH[5] = { 2000, 1000, 300, 100, 50};

10400 void uvsChangeRaiting( void ){
10401 
10402  if (GamerResult.game_result < 1 )
10403  return;
10404 
10405  switch (GamerResult.last_game_type){
10406  case UVS_GAME_ID::ELEECH:
10407  if (V_RACE_VANGER >= GamerResult.game_result)
10408  GamerResult.game_elr_result += GAME_RAITING[ GamerResult.game_result-1];
10409 
10410  if ((GamerResult.game_result-1) < 5)
10411  aciUpdateCurCredits(aciGetCurCredits() + ELEECH[GamerResult.game_result-1]);
10412  break;
10413  case UVS_GAME_ID::PIPETKA:
10414  if (V_RACE_VANGER >= GamerResult.game_result)
10415  GamerResult.game_pip_result += GAME_RAITING[ GamerResult.game_result-1];
10416 
10417  if ((GamerResult.game_result-1) < 3)
10418  aciUpdateCurCredits(aciGetCurCredits() + PIPETKA[GamerResult.game_result-1]);
10419  break;
10420  case UVS_GAME_ID::KERNOBOO:
10421  if (V_RACE_VANGER >= GamerResult.game_result)
10422  GamerResult.game_ker_result += GAME_RAITING[ GamerResult.game_result-1];
10423 
10424  if ((GamerResult.game_result-1) < 3)
10425  aciUpdateCurCredits(aciGetCurCredits() + KERNOBOO[GamerResult.game_result-1]);
10426  break;
10427  case UVS_GAME_ID::WEEZYK:
10428  if (V_RACE_VANGER >= GamerResult.game_result)
10429  GamerResult.game_zyk_result += GAME_RAITING[ GamerResult.game_result-1];
10430 
10431  if ((GamerResult.game_result-1) < 1)
10432  aciUpdateCurCredits(aciGetCurCredits() + WEEZYK[GamerResult.game_result-1]);
10433  break;
10434  }// end switch
10435 }

10441 int uvsGenerateItemForCrypt( int type ){
10442  int itype, icount, _type_;
10443 
10444  switch (type){
10445  case UVS_CRYPT::DEVICE:
10446  itype = UVS_ITEM_TYPE::AMPUTATOR;
10447  icount = UVS_ITEM_TYPE::MECHOSCOPE + 1 - itype;
10448 // icount = 0;
10449  return (itype + RND(icount));
10450  break;
10451  case UVS_CRYPT::ARMO_LIGHT:
10452  itype = UVS_ITEM_TYPE::MACHOTINE_GUN_LIGHT;
10453  icount = UVS_ITEM_TYPE::TERMINATOR2 + 1 - itype;
10454 
10455  _type_ = RND(icount);
10456  while( !uvsItemTable[itype + _type_]->size
10457 #ifdef _DEMO_
10458  || !uvsItemTable[itype + _type_]->count
10459 #endif
10460  )
10461  _type_ = RND(icount);
10462 
10463  return(itype + _type_);
10464  break;
10465  case UVS_CRYPT::ARMO_HEAVY:
10466  itype = UVS_ITEM_TYPE::MACHOTINE_GUN_LIGHT;
10467  icount = UVS_ITEM_TYPE::TERMINATOR2 +1 - itype;
10468 
10469  _type_ = RND(icount);
10470  while( uvsItemTable[itype + _type_]->size
10471 #ifdef _DEMO_
10472  || !uvsItemTable[itype + _type_]->count
10473 #endif
10474  )
10475  _type_ = RND(icount);
10476 
10477  return(itype + _type_);
10478  //pi -> param2 = 8;
10479  break;
10480  case UVS_CRYPT::AMMO:
10481  itype = UVS_ITEM_TYPE::SPEETLE_SYSTEM_AMMO0;
10482  icount = UVS_ITEM_TYPE::GLUEK +1 - UVS_ITEM_TYPE::SPEETLE_SYSTEM_AMMO0;
10483 
10484  _type_ = RND(icount);
10485 #ifdef _DEMO_
10486  if ( type + _type_ == UVS_ITEM_TYPE::CRUSTEST_CANNON_AMMO)
10487  _type_++;
10488 #endif
10489 
10490  return(itype + _type_);
10491  break;
10492  }
10493  return -1;
10494 }

10497  if ( where){
10498  if (what){

10723 int uvsTabuTaskType::is_able(void){
10724  int i;
10725  int world = Gamer -> Pworld -> gIndex;
10726  if ((work_on_target == UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::DELIVER_OR) && (uvsMechosTable[20] -> constractor == 3) )
10727  return 0;
10728 
10729  if (target == UVS_TARGET::RACE) {
10730  for( i = 0; i < item_number; i++ )
10731  if (!uvsCheckItem(item[i]))
10732  return 0;
10733  }
10734 
10735  if ((work_on_target == UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::DELIVER_OR ||
10736  work_on_target == UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::DELIVER_ONE ||
10737  work_on_target == UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::DELIVER) ){
10738  for( i = 0; i < item_number; i++ )
10739  if (!uvsCheckItem(item[i]))
10740  return 0;
10741  }
10742 
10743  switch( priority ){
10744  case 1:
10745  break;
10746  case 2:
10747  if (world == 0 && aciWorldLinkExist(0,1,0) == 0) return 0;
10748  if (world == 1 && dgD -> bStatus < 1) return 0;
10749  if (world == 2 && GamerResult.game_zyk_result == 0) return 0;
10750  break;
10751  case 3:
10752  if (world == 0 && uvsSecretON() == 0) return 0;
10753  if (world == 1 && dgD -> bStatus < 2) return 0;
10754  if (world == 2 && (uvsSecretON() == 0 || GamerResult.game_zyk_result == 0)) return 0;
10755  break;
10756  case 4:
10757  if (world == 0) return 0;
10758  if (world == 1 && (dgD -> bStatus < 2 || uvsSecretON() == 0)) return 0;
10759  if (world == 2) return 0;
10760  break;
10761  }// end switch
10762 
10763  if (Pworld)
10764  return Pworld -> GamerVisit;
10765  else
10766  return 1;
10767 }

10780 uvsPassage* GetPassage(int fromWID, int toWID){

10785

10787  return WorldTable[fromWID] -> pssT[0];
10788  }
10789 
10790  if (toWID >= MAIN_WORLD_MAX ) {
10791  int lastID = toWID;
10792  toWID = WorldTable[toWID] -> pssT[0] -> Poutput -> gIndex;
10793 
10794  if (fromWID == toWID) return WorldTable[fromWID] -> getPassage( getWorld(lastID) );;
10795  }
10796 
10797  unsigned int linkage = ChainMap[toWID + fromWID*MAIN_WORLD_MAX],mI;
10798 
10799 
10800  mI = linkage & (0x0000000F);
10801  nextW = getWorld(mI);
10802 
10803  if(!nextW) nextW = getWorld(toWID);
10804  fromW = getWorld(fromWID);
10805 
10806  return fromW -> getPassage(nextW);
10807 }

10809 uvsVanger* FindFreeVanger(void){
10810  uvsElement* p = ETail;
10811  uvsVanger* v;
10812  while(p){
10813  if(p -> type == UVS_OBJECT::VANGER && ((uvsVanger*)p) -> shape != UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::GAMER){
10814  v = (uvsVanger*)p;
10815  if( v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::SPOT_SLEEPING || v -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::ESCAVE_SLEEPING){
10816  if (Gamer -> Pworld -> escTmax)
10817  v -> Pworld = Gamer -> Pworld;
10818  else
10819  v -> Pworld = WorldTable[RND(3)];
10820 
10821  v -> Pescave = Gamer -> Pescave;
10822  v -> Pspot = Gamer -> Pspot;
10823  v -> shape = UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::TABUTASK;
10824 
10825  if (v -> Pescave ){
10826  v -> pos_x = v -> Pescave -> pos_x + 1024;
10827  v -> pos_y = v -> Pescave -> pos_y + (1-RND(2))*1000;
10828  } else {
10829  v -> pos_x = v -> Pspot -> pos_x + 1024;
10830  v -> pos_y = v -> Pspot -> pos_y + (1-RND(2))*1000;
10831  }
10832  v -> Pworld -> escT[0] -> Pshop -> sellMechos(v -> Pmechos);
10833 
10834  if (!v -> Pmechos)
10835  return NULL;
10836  return v;
10837  }
10838 
10839  }
10840  p = p -> enext;
10841  }
10842  return NULL;
10843 }

10845 void uvsCheckVangerTabuTask(uvsVanger* pv, int how){
10846  int i;
10847 
10848  for( i = 0; i < MAX_TABUTASK; i++){
10849  if (TabuTable[i] -> status == UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::ACTIVE){
10850  switch(TabuTable[i] -> target){
10851  case UVS_TARGET::VANGER:
10852  if ( TabuTable[i] -> Ptarget == ((uvsTarget*)pv) ){
10853 
10854  switch(TabuTable[i] -> work_on_target){
10855  case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::GO_OUT:
10856  if ( how == uvsVANGER_ARRIVAL ){
10857  uvsChangeTabuTask(i, UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::BAD);
10858  TabuTable[i] -> status = UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::SLEEP;
10859  } else {
10860  uvsChangeTabuTask(i, UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::GOOD);
10861  uvsChangeTownTabuTask(i);
10862  TabuTable[i] -> status = UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::OK;
10863  }
10864  pv -> shape = UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::BUNCH_SLAVE;
10865 // TabuTable[i] -> status = UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::SLEEP;
10866  break;
10867  case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::KILL:
10868  if ( how == uvsVANGER_FAILED || how == uvsVANGER_KILLED) {
10869  uvsChangeTabuTask(i, UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::GOOD);
10870  uvsChangeTownTabuTask(i);
10871  pv -> shape = UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::BUNCH_SLAVE;
10872  TabuTable[i] -> status = UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::OK;
10873  }
10874  break;
10875  case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::DEFENSE:
10876  if ( how == uvsVANGER_ARRIVAL ){
10877  uvsChangeTabuTask(i, UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::BAD);
10878  TabuTable[i] -> status = UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::SLEEP;
10879  } else {
10880  uvsChangeTabuTask(i, UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::GOOD);
10881  TabuTable[i] -> status = UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::OK;
10882  uvsChangeTownTabuTask(i);
10883  }
10884  pv -> shape = UVS_VANGER_SHAPE::BUNCH_SLAVE;
10885 // TabuTable[i] -> status = UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::SLEEP;
10886  break;
10887  }// end switch
10888  }// end if
10889  break;
10890  case UVS_TARGET::VANGERS:
10891  if ( how == uvsVANGER_KILLED){
10892  switch(TabuTable[i] -> work_on_target){
10893  case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::KILL:
10894  int NEEDFlag = *TabuTable[i] -> item;
10895  int Mask = 0;
10896 
10897  if (pv -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::RACE)
10898  Mask |= UVS_KRON_FLAG::ELEREC;
10899  else if (pv -> status == UVS_VANGER_STATUS::RACE_HUNTER)
10900  Mask |= UVS_KRON_FLAG::ZEEXL;
10901  else if (CurrentWorld == 1 && uvsCurrentCycle == 1)
10902  Mask |= UVS_KRON_FLAG::PIP;
10903  else if (CurrentWorld == 1 && uvsCurrentCycle == 2)
10904  Mask |= UVS_KRON_FLAG::KERN;
10905 
10906  switch(pv -> Pmechos -> color){
10907  case 0: Mask |= UVS_KRON_FLAG::ELIPOD;
10908  break;
10909  case 1: Mask |= UVS_KRON_FLAG::BEEBO;
10910  break;
10911  case 2: Mask |= UVS_KRON_FLAG::ZEEX;
10912  break;
10913  }// end switch
10914 
10915  int KronFlag = Mask & NEEDFlag;
10916 
10917  if ( ( (NEEDFlag & 0x000000F0) == 0 || (KronFlag & 0x000000F0)) && ( (NEEDFlag & 0x00000F00) == 0 || (KronFlag & 0x00000F00)) ){
10918  (*TabuTable[i] -> real_count)++;
10919 
10920  if ((*TabuTable[i] -> real_count) >= (*TabuTable[i] -> item_count)){
10921  uvsChangeTabuTask(i, UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::GOOD);
10922  uvsChangeTownTabuTask(i);
10923  TabuTable[i] -> status = UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::OK;
10924  *TabuTable[i] -> real_count = 0;
10925  }// end if
10926  }
10927 ;
10928  break;
10929  }// ens switch
10930  }// end if
10931  break;
10932  case UVS_TARGET::RAFFA:
10933  if ( uvsMechosTable[ pv -> Pmechos -> type ] -> type == UVS_CAR_TYPE::RAFFA && how == uvsVANGER_KILLED ){
10934 
10935  (*TabuTable[i] -> real_count)++;
10936 
10937  if ((*TabuTable[i] -> real_count) >= (*TabuTable[i] -> item_count)){
10938  uvsChangeTabuTask(i, UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::GOOD);
10939  uvsChangeTownTabuTask(i);
10940  TabuTable[i] -> status = UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::OK;
10941  *TabuTable[i] -> real_count = 0;
10942  }// end if
10943 
10944  }// end if
10945  break;
10946  }// end switch
10947  }// end if
10948  }// end for i
10949 }

11188 void uvsCheckItemOnTabuTask(listElem*& pe, int ID, int IDcount, int what){
11189  int i, j, komplit;
11190 
11191  for( i = 0; i < MAX_TABUTASK; i++){
11192  if ( TabuTable[i] -> status == UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::ACTIVE){
11193  if ((TabuTable[i] -> target == UVS_TARGET::ITEM) && ( i >= ID ) && ( i < ID + IDcount)){
11194 
11195  switch(TabuTable[i] -> work_on_target){
11196  case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::DELIVER:
11197  case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::DELIVER_ONE:
11198  case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::DELIVER_OR:
11199  if (what){
11200  for( j = 0; j < TabuTable[i] -> item_number; j++){
11201  int l_count = TabuTable[i] -> item_count[j] - TabuTable[i] -> real_count[j];
11202  TabuTable[i] -> real_count[j] += ItemCount(pe, TabuTable[i] -> item[j]);
11203  uvsDeleteItem(pe, TabuTable[i] -> item[j], l_count);
11204 // uvs_aciKillItem(uvsItemTable[ TabuTable[i] -> item[j] ] -> SteelerTypeFull);
11205  }
11206  } else {
11207  for( j = 0; j < TabuTable[i] -> item_number; j++)
11208  TabuTable[i] -> real_count[j] -= ItemCount(pe, TabuTable[i] -> item[j]);
11209  }
11210 
11211  if (!what) break;
11212 
11213  if (TabuTable[i] -> work_on_target != UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::DELIVER_OR){
11214  komplit = 1;
11215 
11216  for( j = 0; j < TabuTable[i] -> item_number; j++)
11217  if (TabuTable[i] -> real_count[j] < TabuTable[i] -> item_count[j])
11218  komplit = 0;
11219  } else {
11220  komplit = 0;
11221 
11222  for( j = 0; j < TabuTable[i] -> item_number; j++)
11223  if (TabuTable[i] -> real_count[j] >= TabuTable[i] -> item_count[j])
11224  komplit = 1;
11225  }
11226 
11227  if (komplit){
11228  uvsChangeTabuTask(i, UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::GOOD);
11229  uvsChangeTownTabuTask(i);
11230  TabuTable[i] -> status = UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::OK;
11231  *TabuTable[i] -> real_count = 0;
11232  }
11233  if (TabuTable[i] -> work_on_target == UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::DELIVER_ONE)
11234  for( j = 0; j < TabuTable[i] -> item_number; j++)
11235  TabuTable[i] -> real_count[j] = 0;
11236  break;
11237  }// end switch
11238  } else if ( (TabuTable[i] -> target == UVS_TARGET::ESCAVE) || (TabuTable[i] -> target == UVS_TARGET::SPOT) ){
11239  int _ID_;
11240 
11241  if (TabuTable[i] -> target == UVS_TARGET::ESCAVE)
11242  _ID_ = ((uvsEscave*)TabuTable[i] -> Ptarget) -> TabuTaskID;
11243  else
11244  _ID_ = ((uvsSpot*)TabuTable[i] -> Ptarget) -> TabuTaskID;
11245 
11246  if (_ID_ == ID){
11247  switch(TabuTable[i] -> work_on_target){
11248  case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::GO_WITHOUT_DAMAGE:
11249  case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::GO_WITHOUT_GRIB:
11250 // case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::GO_FLY:
11251  if (!what) break;
11252  uvsChangeTabuTask(i, UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::GOOD);
11253  uvsChangeTownTabuTask(i);
11254  TabuTable[i] -> status = UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::OK;
11255  *TabuTable[i] -> real_count = 0;
11256  break;
11257  case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::DELIVER:
11258  case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::DELIVER_ONE:
11259  case UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::DELIVER_OR:
11260  if (what){
11261  for( j = 0; j < TabuTable[i] -> item_number; j++){
11262  int l_count = TabuTable[i] -> item_count[j] - TabuTable[i] -> real_count[j];
11263  TabuTable[i] -> real_count[j] += ItemCount(pe, TabuTable[i] -> item[j]);
11264  uvsDeleteItem(pe, TabuTable[i] -> item[j], l_count);
11265 // uvs_aciKillItem(uvsItemTable[ TabuTable[i] -> item[j] ] -> SteelerTypeFull);
11266  }
11267  } else {
11268  for( j = 0; j < TabuTable[i] -> item_number; j++)
11269  TabuTable[i] -> real_count[j] -= ItemCount(pe, TabuTable[i] -> item[j]);
11270  }
11271 
11272  if (!what) break;
11273 
11274  if (TabuTable[i] -> work_on_target != UVS_TABUTASK_WORK::DELIVER_OR){
11275  komplit = 1;
11276 
11277  for( j = 0; j < TabuTable[i] -> item_number; j++)
11278  if (TabuTable[i] -> real_count[j] < TabuTable[i] -> item_count[j])
11279  komplit = 0;
11280  } else {
11281  komplit = 0;
11282 
11283  for( j = 0; j < TabuTable[i] -> item_number; j++)
11284  if (TabuTable[i] -> real_count[j] >= TabuTable[i] -> item_count[j])
11285  komplit = 1;
11286  }
11287

11289  uvsChangeTabuTask(i, UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::GOOD);
11290  uvsChangeTownTabuTask(i);
11291  TabuTable[i] -> status = UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::OK;
11292  *TabuTable[i] -> real_count = 0;
11293  }

11295  for( j = 0; j < TabuTable[i] -> item_number; j++)
11296  TabuTable[i] -> real_count[j] = 0;
11297  break;
11298  }// end switch
11299  }// end if _ID_
11300  }// end if taget
11301  }// end if status
11302  }// end for i

11305 void uvsChangeTabuTask(int type, int status){
11306  uvsActInt *pa = GGamer;
11307 
11308  if (status == UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::BAD){
11309  ShowTaskMessage(-TabuTable[ type ] -> luck);
11310  } else {
11311  ShowTaskMessage(TabuTable[ type] -> luck);
11312  }
11313 
11314  if (GGamer){
11315  while( pa ){
11316  int _type_ = ActInt_to_Item( pa -> type);
11317 
11318  if (_type_ == UVS_ITEM_TYPE::TABUTASK && (pa -> param2 == type)){
11319  pa -> param2 |= (status <<16);
11320 
11321  if (status == UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::BAD){
11322  GamerResult.luck -= TabuTable[ pa -> param2 & 0x0000FFFF] -> luck;
11323  if (GamerResult.luck < 0) GamerResult.luck = 0;
11324  } else {
11325  GamerResult.luck += TabuTable[ pa -> param2 & 0x0000FFFF] -> luck;
11326  if (GamerResult.luck > 100) GamerResult.luck = 100;
11327  }
11328 
11329  if (status == UVS_TABUTASK_STATUS::GOOD){
11330  SOUND_SUCCESS();
11331 // uvs_aciChangeOneItem(pa -> type, TABUTASK_GOOD, pa );
11332  uvs_aciChangeOneItem(pa -> type, TABUTASK_GOOD, pa -> pos_x, pa -> pos_y);
11333 
11334  pa -> type = TABUTASK_GOOD;
11335 
11336  int param2 = pa -> param2 & 0x0000FFFF;
11337 
11338  if (Gamer -> Pescave){
11339  if ( (Gamer -> Pescave -> TabuTaskID <= param2) && (Gamer -> Pescave -> TabuTaskCount +Gamer -> Pescave -> TabuTaskID > param2))
11340  pa -> sell_price = TabuTable[param2] -> cash;
11341  } else {
11342  if ( (Gamer -> Pspot -> TabuTaskID <= param2) && (Gamer -> Pspot -> TabuTaskCount +Gamer -> Pspot -> TabuTaskID > param2))
11343  pa -> sell_price = TabuTable[param2] -> cash;
11344  }
11345  } else {
11346  SOUND_FAILED()
11347  uvs_aciChangeOneItem(pa -> type, TABUTASK_BAD, pa -> pos_x, pa -> pos_y);
11348 // uvs_aciChangeOneItem(pa -> type, TABUTASK_BAD, pa);
11349 
11350  pa -> type = TABUTASK_BAD;
11351  }
11352  }
11353 
11354  pa = (uvsActInt*)(pa -> next);
11355  }// end while
11356  }// end if
11357 
11358  if (uvsKronActive)
11359  ChangeTabutaskItem(type, status);
11360 
11361  uvsWorld *pw = (uvsWorld*)WorldTail;
11362 
11363  while( pw ){
11364  pw -> ChangeTabuTaskInList(type, status);
11365  pw = (uvsWorld*)pw -> next;
11366  }
11367 }

11430 void uvsActIntSellMechos( uvsActInt *pn){
11431  int first_constr = MAX_MECHOS_TYPE - MAX_MECHOS_CONSTRACTOR;
11432  uvsBunch* pm = Gamer -> Pworld -> escT[0] -> Pbunch;
11433 
11434  int cq = pm -> cycleTable[ pm -> currentStage ].cirtQ;
11435  int mq = pm -> cycleTable[ pm -> currentStage ].cirtMAX;
11436 
11437 
11438  if ( ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> type >= first_constr && ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price == 1){
11439  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price = uvsMechosTable[( ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> type)] -> price;
11440 
11441  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price = (((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price*1.5*cq + ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price*(mq-cq))/mq;
11442  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price = (((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price*cq + ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price*0.5*(mq-cq))/mq;
11443 
11444  double t = ((double)(GamerResult.dominance+GamerResult.add_dominance))/100.0;
11445 
11446  if ( t > 1.0 ) t = 1.0;
11447  if ( t < -1.0 ) t = -1.0;
11448 
11449  if ( t > 0.0 ){
11450  double dt = ( ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price - ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price)/2.0;
11451  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price -= t*dt;
11452  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price += t*dt;
11453  } else {
11454  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price *= (1.0 - t);
11455  ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price *= (1.0 + t);
11456  }
11457 
11458  if (((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price > ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price) ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> sell_price = ((uvsActInt*)pn) -> price;
11459  }
11460 }

11522 int uvsGameRaceNumber(void){

11578 int uvsPrepareItemToDiagen(int type, int param1, int param2, int& what, int& ID, char*& NameFrom, char*& NameTo){
11579 
11580  switch(type){
11581  case UVS_ITEM_TYPE::POPONKA:
11582  what = DG_POPONKA;
11583  ID = param2;
11584 
11585  if (ID >= DG_POPONKA_MAX || ID < 0)
11586  ID = 0;
11587 
11588  NameFrom = NULL;
11589  NameTo = NULL;
11590  return 1;
11591  break;
11592  case UVS_ITEM_TYPE::TABUTASK:
11593  what = DG_TABUTASK;
11594 #ifdef _IN_FILE_
11595  ff <= (param2 & 0x0000FFFF) < "\n";
11596 #endif
11597  NameFrom = uvsGetNameByID(param2 & 0x0000FFFF, ID);
11598 #ifdef _IN_FILE_
11599  ff < NameFrom < "\n";
11600 #endif
11601  NameTo = NULL;
11602  ID = (param2 & 0x0000FFFF) - ID;
11603 #ifdef _IN_FILE_
11604  ff <= ID < "\n";
11605 #endif
11606  return 1;
11607  break;
11608  case UVS_ITEM_TYPE::ELEEPOD:
11609  case UVS_ITEM_TYPE::BEEBOORAT:
11610  case UVS_ITEM_TYPE::ZEEX:
11611  what = DG_PASSENGER;
11612  NameFrom = uvsGetNameByID(param2 & 0x0000FFFF, ID);
11613  NameTo = uvsGetNameByID(param2 >>16, ID);
11614  ID = 0;
11615  return 1;
11616  break;
11617  }// end switch
11618  return 0;
11619 }

12034 int uvsWorldToCross(int fromWID, int toWID){
12035  uvsWorld* fromW = WorldTable[fromWID];
12036  uvsWorld* toW = WorldTable[toWID];
12037  uvsWorld* nextW,*tmpW = NULL;
12038  uvsWorld *lastfromW = NULL, *lasttoW = NULL;
12039  uvsPassage* pp;
12040  int i = 0;
12041  int _i_ = 0;
12042 
12043  if ( fromWID == 7 || toWID == 7)
12044  return -1;
12045 
12046  if (fromW -> gIndex >= MAIN_WORLD_MAX ) {
12047  lastfromW = fromW;
12048  fromW = fromW -> pssT[0] -> Poutput;
12049 
12050  _i_ += 1;
12051  }
12052 
12053  if (toW -> gIndex >= MAIN_WORLD_MAX ) {
12054  lasttoW = toW;
12055  toW = toW -> pssT[0] -> Poutput;
12056  _i_ += 1;
12057  }
12058 
12059  unsigned int linkage = ChainMap[toW -> gIndex + fromW -> gIndex*MAIN_WORLD_MAX],mI;
12060 
12061  if ( fromW == toW ) return _i_;
12062 
12063  for(i = 0; i < 8; i++, _i_++){
12064  mI = (linkage & (0x0000000F << 4*i)) >> 4*i;
12065  nextW = getWorld(mI);
12066 
12067  if(!nextW) nextW = toW;
12068  pp = fromW -> getPassage(nextW);
12069 
12070  if ( !pp ) ErrH.Abort( "buildWay:: not passage");
12071 
12072  fromW = nextW;
12073  if ( fromW == toW ) break;
12074  }
12075  _i_++;
12076  return (_i_);
12077 }
